    "name": "Escape The Mad Empire",
    "steam_appid": 1823390,
    "required_age": "16",
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>逃离疯狂帝国</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/5416dcb04a916e56795c6d4315c3cb12.poster.avif?t=1758645973\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/5416dcb04a916e56795c6d4315c3cb12.webm?t=1758645973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/5416dcb04a916e56795c6d4315c3cb12.mp4?t=1758645973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帝国已坠落，幸存者被困在自己制造的末日之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能组建一支英雄队伍，逃离疯狂的帝国吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>召集你的英雄</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/4e62990755de934f1379d1e715cccee4.poster.avif?t=1758645973\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/4e62990755de934f1379d1e715cccee4.webm?t=1758645973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/4e62990755de934f1379d1e715cccee4.mp4?t=1758645973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌握一支多样化英雄队伍的全部潜力，从13个职业中选择。通过技能、装备等解锁他们的最大潜力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>使用疯狂战利品</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/d284eab3ca9e2311f821792a0d041ed8.poster.avif?t=1758645973\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/d284eab3ca9e2311f821792a0d041ed8.webm?t=1758645973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/d284eab3ca9e2311f821792a0d041ed8.mp4?t=1758645973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在疯狂中，帝国利用水晶创造了荒诞且被诅咒的物品。在Escape the Mad Empire中，每一件战利品都既具有意义又极其不稳定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>瞬间制定策略</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/2c0b8697dbfb2658c8a95d79ad66eb79.poster.avif?t=1758645973\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/2c0b8697dbfb2658c8a95d79ad66eb79.webm?t=1758645973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/2c0b8697dbfb2658c8a95d79ad66eb79.mp4?t=1758645973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巧妙地运用你的英雄和他们的物品，在末日中生存下来。随时暂停战斗，立刻使用法术、技能和消耗品，扭转战局！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>打造疯狂机器</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/120a05f72389d68d8d10f72edf12e72a.poster.avif?t=1758645973\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/120a05f72389d68d8d10f72edf12e72a.webm?t=1758645973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/120a05f72389d68d8d10f72edf12e72a.mp4?t=1758645973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的基地是你的避风港。在这里，你可以使用现实水晶来建造强大的机器，这些机器可以帮助你招募、升级或恢复英雄，购买、制作、鉴定或附魔装备，等等。轻松放松，构思最终队伍！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>穿越末日，规划你的道路</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/49e2afeacc0c63287bf1304da4ff00c5.poster.avif?t=1758645973\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/49e2afeacc0c63287bf1304da4ff00c5.webm?t=1758645973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/49e2afeacc0c63287bf1304da4ff00c5.mp4?t=1758645973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次大胆的逃亡尝试，你都将穿越疯狂帝国挖掘出来的深邃迷宫。冒险去冒险，收获丰厚奖励，并在每次挑战的结尾面对强大boss。每次成功逃脱后，英雄们将获得资源，用于发展你的基地，并继续在疯狂帝国的末日中前行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你能逃离疯狂帝国吗？</strong></p>",
